Film Screening by P Sainath [4 Nov 2014, 6pm, Somerville College]

Dear members,

We shall have a film screening by P Sainath titled:

 Journalism from Below: People's Archive of Rural India
 and the Everyday Lives of Everyday People

P Sainath is an acclaimed reporter, Magsaysay Award winner and the author
of 'Everybody Loves a Good Drought'.

Location: Somerville College, Woodstock Road, Oxford
Time: 4 Nov 2014 6pm

Organised with the Oxford India Centre for Sustainable Development.

See the poster for the talk at
http://posters.oxfordindiasociety.org.uk/20141104-p-sainath-film-screening.png

Cheers
Team OIS
